edge: User edits .md -> OS fires FS events | label: save
edge: OS fires FS events -> VaultWatcher | label: inotify / FSEvents
edge: VaultWatcher -> Debouncer (500ms) | label: raw events
edge: Debouncer (500ms) -> EventBus | label: file_changed
edge: EventBus -> Parser | label: triggers
edge: Parser -> Node / Edge | label: creates
edge: Node / Edge -> DB upsert | label: INSERT OR UPDATE
edge: DB upsert -> FTS5 Search | label: triggers sync
edge: DB upsert -> BFS Ego-Graph | label: queryable
edge: BFS Ego-Graph -> RAG Context | label: triples
edge: EventBus -> Git auto-commit | label: file_changed
edge: FTS5 Search -> TUI (Textual) | label: search results
edge: FTS5 Search -> REST API | label: search endpoint
edge: FTS5 Search -> MCP Server | label: search_nodes tool
edge: RAG Context -> MCP Server | label: get_graph_context
